{"type":"message","id":"cab407ca","parentId":"908afb20","timestamp":"2026-04-18T13:22:23.732Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-18 21:22:04 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b510c197008acc363285c5d58bc0]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b510c197008acc363285c5d58bc0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-18 21:22 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n后台安装的skill都有什么"}],"timestamp":1776518543716}}
{"type":"message","id":"0eb22491","parentId":"cab407ca","timestamp":"2026-04-18T13:22:51.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what skills are installed in the background (后台安装的skill). Let me check the available skills listed in the system prompt and also check if there are any installed skills I may not have in my immediate context.\n\nFrom the available_skills section in my system prompt, I can see many skills listed. Let me organize them for the user.\n\nBut wait, the user might be asking about skills installed via clawhub or other means that may not be in my default context. Let me check what skills are actually installed.\n\nActually, looking at the available_skills in my context, these are the skills available to me. Let me list them out in a clean way."},{"type":"text","text":"根据我当前加载的 Skill 清单，已安装的技能（Skills）如下：\n\n---\n\n## 📦 已安装技能列表\n\n### 🌐 通用工具\n| 技能名 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|\n| **Agent Browser** | Rust 无头浏览器自动化，AI 操控网页 |\n| **auto-updater** | 每日自动更新 Clawdbot 和所有已装 Skill |\n| **clawhub** | 搜索/安装/发布 ClawHub 上的技能 |\n| **coding-agent** | 委托任务给 Codex、Claude Code 等编码 Agent |\n| **gemini** | Gemini CLI 一次性问答/总结/生成 |\n| **github** | 通过 `gh` CLI 与 GitHub 交互 |\n| **google-trends** | 监控 Google Trends，热门搜索分析 |\n| **healthcheck** | 主机安全加固与风险配置检查 |\n| **humanizer** | 去除 AI 文风，让文字更自然 |\n| **multi-search-engine** | 17 个搜索引擎集成（中/英） |\n| **openclaw-doctor** | OpenClaw 诊断与修复工具 |\n| **self-improvement** | 记录错误与纠正，持续自我改进 |\n| **skill-creator** | 创建新技能的指南 |\n| **skill-vetter** | 安全审查第三方 Skill |\n| **summarize** | 总结 URL、PDF、图片、音频、YouTube |\n| **tavily-search** | Tavily API 网页搜索 |\n| **vibesurf** | 网页自动化、填表、数据提取 |\n| **weather** | 天气查询（无需 API Key） |\n\n### 🛒 选品相关\n| 技能名 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|\n| **1688-product-search** | 1688 商品搜索（关键词/图片/类目） |\n| **1688-ranking** | 1688 榜单查询（热卖/好价/热搜词） |\n| **alphashop-sel-product-search** | Amazon/TikTok 商品搜索（AlphaShop API） |\n\n### 📅 飞书集成（openclaw-lark 扩展）\n| 技能名 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|\n| **feishu-bitable** | 飞书多维表格创建、查询、编辑 |\n| **feishu-calendar** | 飞书日历与日程管理 |\n| **feishu-channel-rules** | 飞书频道输出规则 |\n| **feishu-create-doc** | 创建飞书云文档 |\n| **feishu-fetch-doc** | 获取飞书云文档内容 |\n| **feishu-im-read** | 读取飞书 IM 消息、话题、搜索 |\n| **feishu-task** | 飞书任务/待办管理 |\n| **feishu-troubleshoot** | 飞书插件问题排查 |\n| **feishu-update-doc** | 更新飞书云文档（7 种模式） |\n| **飞书多 Agent 配置助手** | 交互式多 Agent 系统配置 |\n\n### 🔧 内部编排\n| 技能名 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|\n| **node-connect** | 节点连接与配对问题诊断 |\n| **taskflow** | 跨任务流编排与状态管理 |\n| **taskflow-inbox-triage** | 收件箱分流模式示例 |\n\n---\n\n共 **28 个 Skill** 已加载。飞书相关技能由 `openclaw-lark` 扩展提供，选品相关由 `workspace/.agents/skills` 提供，其余为全局通用技能。\n\n有想了解或安装新的 Skill 可以告诉我。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776518543734,"responseId":"0632b89086311a2e03b5467b4ddf486f"}}
