on and      │ openclaw-bundled      │\n│               │                                 │ pairing failures for Android, iOS, and     │                       │\n│               │                                 │ macOS companion apps. Use when QR/setup    │                       │\n│               │                                 │ code/manual connect fails, local Wi-Fi     │                       │\n│               │                                 │ works but VPS/tailnet does not, or errors  │                       │\n│               │                                 │ mention pairing required, unauthorized,    │                       │\n│               │                                 │ bootstrap token invalid or expired,        │                       │\n│               │                                 │ gateway.bind, gateway.remote.url,          │                       │\n│               │                                 │ Tailscale, or plugins.entries.device-pair. │                       │\n│               │                                 │ config.publicUrl.                          │                       │\n│ △ needs setup │ 📝 notion                       │ Notion API for creating and managing       │ openclaw-bundled      │\n│               │                                 │ pages, databases, and blocks.              │                       │\n│ △ needs setup │ 💎 obsidian                     │ Work with Obsidian vaults (plain Markdown  │ openclaw-bundled      │\n│               │                                 │ notes) and automate via obsidian-cli.      │                       │\n│ △ needs setup │ 🎤 openai-whisper               │ Local speech-to-text with the Whisper CLI  │ openclaw-bundled      │\n│               │                                 │ (no API key).                              │                       │\n│ △ needs setup │ 🌐 openai-whisper-api           │ Transcribe audio via OpenAI Audio          │ openclaw-bundled      │\n│            