{"type":"message","id":"c16be410","parentId":"014403d5","timestamp":"2026-04-18T13:33:00.206Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ibfvwxw0ndat_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.openviking: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\n- plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.15 (041266a) — I've survived more breaking changes than your last three relationships.\n\nUsage: openclaw skills [options] [command]\n\nList and inspect available skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check which skills are ready vs missing requirements\n  info        Show detailed information about a skill\n  install     Install a skill from ClawHub into the active workspace\n  list        List all available skills\n  search      Search ClawHub skills\n  update      Update ClawHub-installed skills in the active workspace\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/skills\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"vivid-sage","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.openviking: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\n- plugins.entries.memory-lancedb: plugin disabled (disabled in config) but config is present\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.15 (041266a) — I've survived more breaking changes than your last three relationships.\n\nUsage: openclaw skills [options] [command]\n\nList and inspect available skills\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check which skills are ready vs missing requirements\n  info        Show detailed information about a skill\n  install     Install a skill from ClawHub into the active workspace\n  list        List all available skills\n  search      Search ClawHub skills\n  update      Update ClawHub-installed skills in the active workspace\n\nDocs: htt