{"type":"message","id":"2de8e63b","parentId":"d06de6b7","timestamp":"2026-04-18T13:33:56.733Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the picture clearly. Let me understand the structure:\n\n1. **Global npm skills** (`~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/`): These are bundled with the npm package and are read-only. The skills listed there include things like `1password`, `apple-notes`, `blogwatcher`, `clawhub`, `coding-agent`, `gemini`, etc. These cannot be \"uninstalled\" by the user as they come with the package.\n\n2. **Workspace skills** (`~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/`): These are user-installed skills in the workspace. They can potentially be removed. These include:\n   - `agent-browser`\n   - `auto-updater`\n   - `feishu-multi-agent-manager`\n   - `github`\n   - `humanizer`\n   - `multi-search-engine`\n   - `openclaw-backup`\n   - `openclaw-repair`\n   - `openclaw-tavily-search`\n   - `polymarket-trade`\n   - `self-improving-agent`\n   - `skill-creator`\n   - `skill-vetter`\n   - `Summarize`\n   - `weather`\n\n3. **Agent-specific skills** (`~/.openclaw/workspace/.agents/skills/`): These are agent-level skills, which can be installed or removed. They currently include `1688-product-search`, `1688-ranking`, `alphashop-sel-product-search`, and `google-trends`.\n\nSo the user's request to \"uninstall\" the 1688 and alphashop skills means I should delete the directories at `~/.openclaw/workspace/.agents/skills/1688-product-search`, `~/.openclaw/workspace/.agents/skills/1688-ranking`, and `~/.openclaw/workspace/.agents/skills/alphashop-sel-product-search`.\n\nFor the `openclaw-doctor` and `self-improvement` skills, those are built-in bundled skills from the npm installation, so they can't be uninstalled. The workspace-level `openclaw-repair` and `self-improving-agent` are different—they're not the same as the built-in versions. But wait, the user asked for `openclaw-doctor`, not `openclaw-repair`, so those built-in skills can't be removed, though the workspace-level duplicates could be deleted if needed."},{"type":"text","text":"了解了。要卸载的是这 5 个：\n\n- `1688-product-search`\n- `1688-ranking`\n- `alphashop-sel-product-search`\n- `openclaw-doctor`\n- `self-improvement`\n\n---\n\n**先说明：** `openclaw-doctor` 和 `self-improvement` 是 **npm 包内置的 Skill**（`openclaw-bundled`），跟随 npm 包更新，走的是只读目录，无法通过删除文件卸载。如果你不再想让我使用它们，可以在配置里禁用。\n\n但 workspace 级别的选品三件套可以删：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j2d4hi63zzt9_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"trash ~/.openclaw/workspace/.agents/skills/1688-product-search ~/.openclaw/workspace/.agents/skills/1688-ranking ~/.openclaw/workspace/.agents/skills/alphashop-sel-product-search 2>&1 && echo \"done\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776519220510,"responseId":"0632bb3551cbf9534fd7890e755c2fd0"}}
