{"type":"message","id":"47c195d6","parentId":"21afb567","timestamp":"2026-04-18T14:54:27.190Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2jytma2wsc0j_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"assets\nCONTRIBUTING.md\nexamples\nindex.js\nLICENSE\nmemory\nnode_modules\npackage.json\npackage-lock.json\nREADME.ja-JP.md\nREADME.md\nREADME.zh-CN.md\nscripts\nSKILL.md\nsrc\ntest\n---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```\n\nOr use as part of OpenClaw skill system.\n\n## Configuration\nSet evolution strategy via environment variable:\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced` (default, recommend)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=innovate` (max innovation)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden` (enhance security)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=repair-only` (only fix errors)\n\n## Offline Mode"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"assets\nCONTRIBUTING.md\nexamples\nindex.js\nLICENSE\nmemory\nnode_modules\npackage.json\npackage-lock.json\nREADME.ja-JP.md\nREADME.md\nREADME.zh-CN.md\nscripts\nSKILL.md\nsrc\ntest\n---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```\n\nOr use as part of OpenClaw skill system.\n\n## Configuration\nSet evolution strategy via environment variable:\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced` (default, recommend)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=innovate` (max innovation)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden` (enhance security)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=repair-only` (only fix errors)\n\n## Offline Mode","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776524067178}}
